The paper focuses on analyzing the spectra of the Conjugate Kernel and the Neural Tangent Kernel, which are related to the initialization and training of neural networks. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and specifically, the sub-categories of neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and signal processing (cs.SI).
